Tk::TextANSIColor
-----------------

Tk::TextANSIColor provides a sub-classed Tk::Text widget that 
understands ANSI color codes.

The ANSI color codes are replaced by tags in the Text widget.

Requirements
------------

Requires perl/Tk and Term::ANSIColor modules.

Has been tested with perl 5.004_04/5.005_03 on Linux RedHat5.2
and Sparc Solaris 2.6 and Tk800.014.

Installation
------------

This is a standard perl module. To install:

  % perl Makefile.PL
  % make
  % make test
  % make install

Currently only one test is available which simply loads the module
and exits.

